primary.context: Caller is having trouble with a registration code and not receiving verification texts.
primary.detail: The agent verified the caller and sent a new Clubhouse registration link via text and email to updated contact information provided by the user.

steps: Agent identifies caller via phone lookup.
Agent performs full name and state verification.
Caller explains technical issues with existing Clubhouse code and SMS verification.
Agent offers to send a new registration link.
Caller provides a different phone number and email address for delivery.
Agent confirms the link is being sent and ends the call.

clarifications.note: Agent asks for spelling of name for accuracy.

corrections.note: User provides a different phone number than the one on file.

actions.detail: Sent link to new phone and email provided.

insights.summary: The caller was unable to register for the Clubhouse portal due to SMS delivery issues; the agent successfully verified her and sent a new link to a different number/email.
insights.verbatim: I put the code in and everything, but nothing is working. When I tried to get it to do the verify your phone number... I never did get a text.
